originalText.text: Alicia is a fantastic life coach. She empowers her clients and helps them recognize how amazing they are. Thank you, Alicia, for showing me that my emotions are valid and that I have the right to express them. I would absolutely suggest it to others.

text.text: Alicia is a fantastic life coach. She empowers her clients and helps them recognize how amazing they are. Thank you, Alicia, for showing me that my emotions are valid and that I have the right to express them. I would absolutely suggest it to others.

originalText.text: If you need a life coach, I HIGHLY recommend Alicia. She is highly insightful, eloquent, and results-oriented. Alicia assisted me in bringing my wants/needs to the surface and putting strategies in place to help me reach my goals during a transitional phase in my life. She dug deep into the issues/dilemmas I was dealing with in order to enable me to embrace my true self. She is incredible:)

originalText.text: I'm grateful to Alicia for assisting me during a difficult period in my life! She is approachable, nonjudgmental, and provides helpful comments. I received excellent advise and techniques to assist me in dealing with anxiety, stress, and becoming more attentive in my daily life. She makes approaching tasks less daunting by dividing them down into manageable steps. If you're thinking about giving life coaching a shot, you'll have a fantastic time with Alicia!

originalText.text: Alicia is a confidence booster extraordinaire! Her counsel has helped me overcome self-doubt and accept my actual potential. She is a great cheerleader and mentor on the path to self-assurance.
